comments.body:
@pkliczewski SGTM,  I  think we would need another pod **field** in podman. As right now it shows if a `pod` is `Running, Created, Exited, Stopped, Dead` there is no **Ready** field like `kubernetes`.  

>When multiple containers are booting and some depend on others with readiness probe it would be easy to understand whether application would work as a whole.

This is a fair request I agree if `n/n` containers are ready in theory application should work.
